<h2>Online Help for CASH BOOK Object</h2>
<br></br> <br></br>    
This is an Object to manage Cash handling at accounting team.<br></br>
<ul>
1. Staff who bring cash to the vendor and how much handed over to the staff<br></br> 
2. Actual paid to vendor against invoice received and evidences from the vendor<br></br>
3. Balance collected after actual cash payment<br></br>
</ul>
<br></br>

Relation with other objects<br></br>
When the H B/L SELLING・BUYING is chosen for cash settlement, <br></br>
AMOUNT BUYING INCLUDING TAX(LOCAL) in H B/L Selling/Buying and H B/L Shipment ID and H B/L Number or HAWB Number is automatically refered.<br></br>

 <br></br>
